TO CHECK DEVICES CONNECTED:
 $ lsusb
 $ lsusb | grep Xbox

TO OPEN THE PORTS:
 $ ls usb ttyUSB*
 $ sudo chmod 777 /dev/ttyUSB0

TO LAUNCH KINECT:
 $ roslaunch openn_launch openni.launch
Bootsrapping Kinect:
 $ roslaunch turtlebot_bringup minimal.launch

TO LAUNCH CAMERA:
 $ rosrun image_view image_view image:=/camera/rgb/image_color
 $ rosrun image_view image_view image:=/camera/depth/image

TO LAUNCH RVIZ:
 $ roslaunch turtlebot_rviz_launchers view_robot.launch

TO LAUNCH TELE-OP:
 $ roslaunch turtlebot_teleop keyboard_teleop.launch

TO Start the SSH and Network:
 $  sudo service ssh status
 $ ifconfig
 $ sudo ssh minha@ipaddressrobot

To change the parameters of the follower:
 $ rosrun rqt_reconfigure rqt_reconfigure







RANDOM USEFUL COMMANDS:

 $ rostopic echo /laptop_charge 
//for the battery status of the laptop



